messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to repent of all sins that I have been involved with all sexual sins I want cleansing and deliverance from all sexual sins I want my spirit cleansed from all the sins that I have been involved in I want the sins out of my heart I surrender all sins to the feet of Jesus I want my eyes opened to spiritual eyes I want to repent to God and I want deliverance from all ungodliness and all idols and sin that separate me from God and holiness
